  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966150/extras/705856128705c8edcfef7be20d901ee8.avif?t=1773123806\" width=612 height=126 /></span><br><br>Defeat all those who seek your power and become even stronger! Magic Venue is an action roguelike game where you must become as strong as you can! Reach the last minute and defeat the bosses of each level! Only then can you prove your worth! During combat, your character will be teleported to various dimensions, you never know what to expect! From losing powers to becoming completely 3D, the dimensions will leave you amazed!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966150/extras/a8a13bbab70d9cc124e24943069dbd9b.poster.avif?t=1773123806\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966150/extras/a8a13bbab70d9cc124e24943069dbd9b.webm?t=1773123806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966150/extras/a8a13bbab70d9cc124e24943069dbd9b.mp4?t=1773123806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966150/extras/a48c5d9a792071e4f0726889c88bd974.webp?t=1773123806\" width=613 height=50 /></span><br>- Confront waves of strange, strong, and bizarre enemies!<br>- Utilize your skills to collect cards and assemble your unique deck!<br>- Use the dimensions to your advantage and devise strategies to win!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966150/extras/1df75be6e8a630cdac14e6d7474e5332.poster.avif?t=1773123806\" width=600 heigh